# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# web-security-snippets — .gitignore
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Python ───────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
share/python-wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg
.env
.venv
env/
venv/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/
.mypy_cache/
.dmypy.json
dmypy.json
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# ── Node.js ──────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*
.pnp/
.pnp.js
.yarn/cache
.yarn/unplugged
.yarn/build-state.yml
.yarn/install-state.gz
dist/
build/
.next/
out/
.nuxt/
.cache/

# ── Go ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.test
*.out
go.sum
vendor/

# ── Java / Maven / Gradle ────────────────────────────────
target/
*.class
*.jar
*.war
*.ear
*.nar
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar
hs_err_pid*
replay_pid*
.gradle/
build/
.mvn/

# ── Rust ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
Cargo.lock
**/*.rs.bk

# ── Ruby ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.gem
*.rbc
/.config
/coverage/
/InstalledFiles
/pkg/
/spec/reports/
/spec/examples.txt
/test/tmp/
/test/version_tmp/
/tmp/
.bundle/
vendor/bundle
Gemfile.lock

# ── C# / .NET ────────────────────────────────────────────
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]in/
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

# ── PHP / Composer ───────────────────────────────────────
vendor/
composer.lock
.phpunit.cache/

# ── Environment and secrets ──────────────────────────────
# These must NEVER be committed — this is a security repo.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development
.env.test
.env.production
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
*.csr
*.der
secrets.json
secrets.yml
secrets.yaml
*secret*
*credential*
*password*
*private_key*

# ── Certificates (for TLS snippets — use examples only) ──
# Real certificates must never be committed
# The tls-config/ folder uses placeholder/example certs only
# *.pem — excluded above

# ── IDE and editor files ─────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Test artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────
coverage/
*.lcov
.nyc_output/
htmlcov/
.coverage
.coverage.*
junit*.xml
test-results/

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# ── Temporary files ──────────────────────────────────────
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp
*.bak
*.backup
*.orig

# ── Docker ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Do not ignore Dockerfiles — they are part of snippets
# Ignore only local Docker data
.docker/

# ── OS specific ──────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
